<%= "Hello #{@application.firstname}," %>
<%= "\r\n" %>
Congratulations! I am writing to inform you that you have been 
admitted into the <%= current_camp_year %> Michigan Math and 
Science Scholars (MMSS) summer program held at the University 
of Michigan in Ann Arbor! 
<%= "\r\n" %>
In order to finalize your admission, please log in to <%= @url %> to accept or decline your admission. 
<%= "\r\n" %>
<%= @offer_letter_text.html_safe %>
<%= "\r\n" %>
=======================================
<%= "\r\n" %>
You have been assigned to:
<%= "\r\n" %>
<% @assigned_sessions.each do |as| %>
  <%= as.camp_occurrence.display_name %>
  <%= "\r\n" %>
<% end %>
<%= "\r\n" %>
To participate in:
<%= "\r\n" %>
<% @assigned_courses.each do |ac| %>
  <%= ac.course.display_name %>
  <%= "\r\n" %>
<% end %>
Your application deadline: <%= @enrollment.application_deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>
<%= "\r\n" %>
=======================================
<%= "\r\n" %>
Please visit your application at <%= @url %>, and accept or decline this offer.